to 300 milligrams of Thorazine?
It's impossible.

68
00:08:57,901 --> 00:08:59,781
That's why
they sent him to you.

69
00:08:59,987 --> 00:09:02,347
Terrific.

70
00:09:02,574 --> 00:09:05,774
