Why is a soap bubble round?

135
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:54,240
Why is a soap bubble round?

136
00:12:54,457 --> 00:12:57,857
You know, for an educated
person, Mark, you repeat
things quite a bit.

137
00:12:58,125 --> 00:13:00,405
Are you aware of that?

138
00:13:02,548 --> 00:13:04,748
A soap bubble is round...

139
00:13:04,926 --> 00:13:08,526
because it is the most
energy-efficient configuration.

140
00:13:09,847 --> 00:13:13,327
Similarly, on your planet,
I look like you.

141
00:13:13,561 --> 00:13:15,921
On K-PAX,
I look like a K-PAXian.

142
00:13:16,106 --> 00:13:18,546
Prot,

143
00:13:18,733 --> 00:13:21,133
why did you want to
come to our planet?

144
00:13:22,571 --> 00:13:25,251
Well, I've been here
many times before.

145
00:13:25,490 --> 00:13:28,850
But what brought me
here first? I don't know.

146
00:13:29,076 --> 00:13:31,516
Pure curiosity, I guess.

147
00:13:31,705 --> 00:13:34,745
I'd never been to
a Class BA-3 planet before.

148
00:13:35,000 --> 00:13:36,960
Class BA-3?

149
00:13:37,170 --> 00:13:38,970
Early stage of evolution.

150
00:13:39,172 --> 00:13:42,252
Future uncertain.

151
00:13:42,508 --> 00:13:45,388
And if I give all my possessions
to feed the poor--

152
00:13:45,596 --> 00:13:49,396
Howie. Go on.
Talk to him.

153
00:13:49,643 --> 00:13:52,443
Go on.

154
00:13:52,646 --> 00:13:55,726
You're really from...
up there?

155
00:13:57,151 --> 00:13:58,991
Indeed.

156
00:14:00,529 --> 00:14:02,929
I am from K-PAX.

157
00:14:03,115 --> 00:14:05,595
What--

158
00:14:05,828 --> 00:14:08,268
What sort of place is it?

159
00:14:08,454 --> 00:14:11,094
