Agape and Satori.

166
00:15:06,186 --> 00:15:09,946
You finish
Your homework, Abby?
Yeah.

167
00:15:10,189 --> 00:15:12,109
I lost another tooth.

168
00:15:12,317 --> 00:15:15,957
Oh, yeah? Let me see.
Hey! Maybe the tooth fairy
will come tonight, huh?

169
00:15:16,197 --> 00:15:18,277
There's no such thing
as the tooth fairy, Dad.

170
00:15:18,491 --> 00:15:20,771
There’s just you and Mom.

171
00:15:20,993 --> 00:15:24,833
I fed them already.
I couldn't wait.
How was your day?

172
00:15:25,122 --> 00:15:29,322
Oh, 6:15 was late.
Didn't leave the station
til 6.:30.

173
00:15:29,584 --> 00:15:31,424
Should have caught
the nearest beam of light.

174
00:15:31,589 --> 00:15:33,429
You should have caught what?

175
00:15:33,591 --> 00:15:36,031
Oh, nothing.
How was your day?
Good.

176
00:15:36,220 --> 00:15:39,940
Sent the deposit in
for the house on the cape for
the last two weeks of August.

177
00:15:40,181 --> 00:15:42,941
Which works out perfectly,
'cause Abby doesn't get out
of camp till the 1 5th.

178
00:15:43,185 --> 00:15:44,985
Sent the deposit in?

179
00:15:45,187 --> 00:15:47,107
Yeah.
Come on, Rache.

180
00:15:47,314 --> 00:15:50,554
That wasn't definite.
We were just talking.
I said maybe.

181
00:15:50,775 --> 00:15:52,975
Maybe sometime in August
we'll clear it.

182
00:15:53,195 --> 00:15:56,675
Maybe. Maybe we should start
paying you for your time.
You got a family rate?

183
00:15:56,908 --> 00:16:00,188
Oh, look.
They published my letter.

184
00:16:02,037 --> 00:16:05,437
I spoke with Natalie about going
into the after-school program
next year,

185
00:16:05,709 --> 00:16:08,109
in case
I go back to teaching.

186
00:16:08,339 --> 00:16:12,059
And this morning my head
fell off, but I was able to sew
it back on with dental floss.

187
00:16:12,343 --> 00:16:15,943
Waxed, of course.
Dental floss?

188
00:16:16,222 --> 00:16:18,022
Sorry.
I wasn't l listening.

189
00:16:18,224 --> 00:16:20,144
Yeah, I know.
Let's just eat.

190
00:16:22,186 --> 00:16:24,666
Train was late.
I'm tired.

191
00:16:24,897 --> 00:16:27,257
