the city is dumping
patients on us.

192
00:16:27,442 --> 00:16:29,762
I know.

193
00:16:36,368 --> 00:16:38,048
You stink.

194
00:16:40,246 --> 00:16:42,566
Have a nice day, Sal.

195
00:16:42,751 --> 00:16:45,711
I've been to 64pLanets
