196
00:16:45,922 --> 00:16:49,962
Earth is the only one
with your species, Homo sapiens,
that I've visited so far.

197
00:16:50,259 --> 00:16:52,059
And when did you arrive
on Earth?

198
00:16:52,261 --> 00:16:54,261
Four years and nine months ago.

199
00:16:54,431 --> 00:16:56,271
So that makes you how old?

200
00:16:56,433 --> 00:16:59,273
In Earth terms, 337 years old.

201
00:16:59,477 --> 00:17:03,597
I aged about seven getting here,
traveling at six multiples
of "C."

202
00:17:03,856 --> 00:17:06,656
But really, Marko,
it only seemed like an instant.

203
00:17:06,860 --> 00:17:11,380
Marko? Time may warp
at super light speed.

204
00:17:11,655 --> 00:17:14,735
I'd say
access one psychosis NOS.

205
00:17:14,952 --> 00:17:18,632
That's glib to
call him a psychotic.
That's a wastebasket diagnosis.

206
00:17:18,917 --> 00:17:22,077
Oh, yeah?
He believes he traveled
here from another planet.

207
00:17:22,294 --> 00:17:24,334
What's your diagnosis,
jet lag?

208
00:17:24,506 --> 00:17:26,866
Well, how come he didn't
respond to the Haldol?

209
00:17:27,092 --> 00:17:28,892
Haldol can make you
more psychotic.

210
00:17:29,094 --> 00:17:31,254
It's rare,
but it does happen.

211
00:17:31,470 --> 00:17:35,710
Look. I'm not saying
that medication can't be
a useful tool...

212
00:17:35,977 --> 00:17:38,257
to help somebody like this,
but you can't--

213
00:17:38,479 --> 00:17:42,159
He maybe a good subject
for the "Betazine" protocol.
The drug's on clinical trial.

214
00:17:42,398 --> 00:17:44,998
You want to experiment on him
before we have a diagnosis?

215
00:17:45,194 --> 00:17:47,354
Do you have some other idea?

216
00:17:47,531 --> 00:17:51,331
He's not a danger to anyone.
How about getting
to know him first?

217
00:17:51,575 --> 00:17:55,135
In the meantime,
we have ten new transfers
to take care of.

218
00:17:55,373 --> 00:17:58,333
You know, maybe what's
wrong with him...

219
00:17:58,543 --> 00:18:01,543
