has been worth the trip.

223
00:18:55,313 --> 00:18:58,593
Could you tell me...

224
00:18:58,818 --> 00:19:01,898
a bit about your boyhood
on K-PAX?

225
00:19:02,111 --> 00:19:03,951
Where were you born?

226
00:19:05,117 --> 00:19:08,997
You were, uh,
born, right?

227
00:19:09,247 --> 00:19:11,087
K-PAXians have babies?

228
00:19:11,248 --> 00:19:13,688
Oh, yes, much like on Earth,
but unlike you humans,

229
00:19:13,918 --> 00:19:17,398
the reproductive process
is quite unpleasant for us.

230
00:19:17,673 --> 00:19:19,913
Could you compare
the effect to something
that I might understand?

231
00:19:20,090 --> 00:19:22,970
Like a toothache?
It's more like having
your nuts in a vlse,

232
00:19:23,177 --> 00:19:25,017
except we feel it all over.

233
00:19:25,181 --> 00:19:27,501
And to make matters worse,
the sensation is associated...

234
00:19:27,724 --> 00:19:31,084
with something like your nausea,
accompanied by a very bad smell.

235
00:19:31,311 --> 00:19:34,431
The moment of climax is like
being kicked in the stomach,

236
00:19:34,648 --> 00:19:37,528
